{"tid":1055771,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪得我覺得captain marvel啲詭族係好人？","createTime":"2019-03-10T18:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T16:38:37.000Z","uid":146340,"like":28,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bf94c38778a2b7545098e16d1bd8fca701feea19","tid":1055771,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"人地係一個科技發達 又和平嘅文明 <br />\n<br />\n跟住你見佢地又有黑鬼又有白鬼都知佢地唯才是用 唔係亂咁歧視<br />\n<br />\n班綠色人 見到軍人第一件事就陰陰濕濕打9人 又搞人潛意識 好明顯有問題<br />\n<br />\n又話自己係難民 明明自己就犯晒罪 跟住就想借人地啲科技去其他星球蝦蝦霸霸<br />\n<br />\n洗女權隊長腦都係迫於無奈 見佢咁能左膠又明顯有情緒病 唔通真係由佢橫行霸道咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以結論就係壞人贏咗 marvel世界好人又輸一仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e8a1ffebd903babeaf4a1889b65e710a4ef366","tid":1055771,"uid":3852,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:09:29.000Z","msg":"咁樣劇透法真係第一次見"},{"pid":"1a8206a3882cf0e365da817033b9af1604226d76","tid":1055771,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"36e8a1ffebd903babeaf4a1889b65e710a4ef366","tid":1055771,"uid":3852,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:09:29.000Z","msg":"咁樣劇透法真係第一次見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:15:32.000Z","msg":"沒有劇透"},{"pid":"1f01de6a80d6884c1372792801280c94e13561eb","tid":1055771,"uid":188282,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T20:23:55.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔明服從詭族有咩問題?<br />\n係咪會抽重稅?<br />\n捉你做苦工定點?"},{"pid":"c042afc23395e5306ccfff21e40301ecfdee49f2","tid":1055771,"uid":1818,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"1f01de6a80d6884c1372792801280c94e13561eb","tid":1055771,"uid":188282,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T20:23:55.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔明服從詭族有咩問題?<br />\n係咪會抽重稅?<br />\n捉你做苦工定點?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T20:42:15.000Z","msg":"香港歸化中國有咩問題<br />\n係咪要做苦工？<br />\n自由阿屌你"},{"pid":"9c2cb58de16a6a6312753ae8ef